{
  "stem": "3449.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was a ghetto [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] without borders, without fences.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a designated ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you knew where you were supposed to be living, and past that area you're not-- you're not allowed to get out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even though we lived-- they also let us live in our own home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't throw us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was separated by-- by a water from the ghetto and the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yet we lived in that little area, as I said before, a [? village ?] there in comparison to the city.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So there was also a little ghetto there they let us live, and-- and the ghetto in the main city.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Almost like two ghettos within the same city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, that was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- the minute you were out past that area you were like-- now it's hunting season, so forget about that.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The one that-- the ones that tried to say, well-- that we-- we left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's how we survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had to take the chance, because we knew liquidation was coming.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And sure enough, it came in four days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But just to leave for the sake of leaving?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No way.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never a problem, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah, some people were hungrier than others.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was-- the ones who were uprooted from their area and thrown into the ghetto, naturally.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to live on handouts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But people helped each other.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We never-- our own family, and most of our area never had problems because the Ukrainians, the farmers, the Polish farmers, the Czech farmers, still kept coming in, like they did before the invasion, to deal and barter.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Most of the stuff was-- was on barter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not quite, but almost.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, we weren't starved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We weren't starved.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
